title: All Your Love
lyrics:
haseena tu kameena mn...
haseena tu kameena mn...

hye mosam tu...
maheena main...
haseena tu kameena mn...



daikhon mn jidher

har aik mor par

nazar ae qeemti nagena

aik pe magar tu therta kidher

tu hy aisa waisa aik kameena...

oo itna bura bhi nhi hy kameena...

aa chal pehchan ly jo tu...

haseena tu kameena mn...

haseena tu kameena mn...



hye mosam tu ...

mahena main...



haseena tu kameena mn...



ooo manmanian...

ooo bemanian...

teri khata hy.

haseenon ko pata hy...



dont you know dont you know



phir bhi dil apna ...

dewanon se uljhna.



haseenon ki ada hy...

mujhy bhi pata hy ...

dont you know dont you know?



jabeeha tu (i love u cutti) tabeena mn(2)



haseena tu kameena mn

haseena tu kameena mn



hye mosam tu ...

maheena main...



haseena tu kameena mn

haseena tu kameena mn

mosam tu...

maheena main...



haseena tu kameena mn

whistle
